{"nodeType":"document","data":{},"content":[{"nodeType":"paragraph","data":{},"content":[{"nodeType":"text","value":"Software testing is becoming more complex, especially with the rise of AI-driven products and large-scale systems. Teams need tools that don’t just collect test results but help them understand and act on the data.","marks":[],"data":{}}]},{"nodeType":"paragraph","data":{},"content":[{"nodeType":"text","value":"ReportPortal brings order to testing chaos — it stores, analyzes, and visualizes results in real time, helping teams improve quality, reduce manual work, and make smarter decisions.","marks":[],"data":{}}]},{"nodeType":"paragraph","data":{},"content":[{"nodeType":"text","value":"blueBg Explore our ","marks":[],"data":{}},{"nodeType":"hyperlink","data":{"uri":"https://reportportal.io/pricing/saas"},"content":[{"nodeType":"text","value":"pricing plans","marks":[{"type":"underline"}],"data":{}}]},{"nodeType":"text","value":" to see how easily you can get started. ","marks":[],"data":{}}]},{"nodeType":"paragraph","data":{},"content":[{"nodeType":"text","value":"Below are some of the key ways ReportPortal supports the AI and software sector.","marks":[],"data":{}}]},{"nodeType":"paragraph","data":{},"content":[{"nodeType":"text","value":"1. AI Model Testing","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"data":{}}]},{"nodeType":"paragraph","data":{},"content":[{"nodeType":"text","value":"The EU AI Act and the U.S. NIST AI Risk Management Framework set new expectations for how AI models should be tested and validated. These checks — such as measuring accuracy or response quality — might not look like traditional functional testing, but they’re essential for reliability and compliance.","marks":[],"data":{}}]},{"nodeType":"paragraph","data":{},"content":[{"nodeType":"text","value":"ReportPortal helps keep these evaluations organized. It doesn’t just store test logs — it lets teams track and compare how a model performs over time using the ","marks":[],"data":{}},{"nodeType":"hyperlink","data":{"uri":"https://reportportal.io/docs/work-with-reports/HistoryOfLaunches/#cell-preview-options"},"content":[{"nodeType":"text","value":"history table","marks":[{"type":"underline"}],"data":{}}]},{"nodeType":"text","value":". For example, you can record model accuracy or response quality as attributes and easily see how these values change across different versions. This makes it easier to track how the model performs over time, keep results consistent, and have everything well-documented in case you need to review or audit the testing later.","marks":[],"data":{}}]},{"nodeType":"paragraph","data":{},"content":[{"nodeType":"text","value":"2. Integration with CI/CD Pipelines and Bug Tracking","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"data":{}}]},{"nodeType":"paragraph","data":{},"content":[{"nodeType":"text","value":"ReportPortal integrates into continuous integration and delivery ","marks":[],"data":{}},{"nodeType":"hyperlink","data":{"uri":"https://reportportal.io/docs/quality-gates/IntegrationWithCICD/"},"content":[{"nodeType":"text","value":"(CI/CD)","marks":[{"type":"underline"}],"data":{}}]},{"nodeType":"text","value":" pipelines to streamline automated testing for system software.","marks":[],"data":{}}]},{"nodeType":"paragraph","data":{},"content":[{"nodeType":"text","value":"This means that every time new code or features are built, test results are automatically collected, analyzed, and displayed in one place. Teams can instantly see which parts of the system passed, failed, or require attention.","marks":[],"data":{}}]},{"nodeType":"paragraph","data":{},"content":[{"nodeType":"text","value":"It also supports integration with ","marks":[],"data":{}},{"nodeType":"hyperlink","data":{"uri":"https://reportportal.io/docs/plugins/bug-tracking/"},"content":[{"nodeType":"text","value":"bug tracking","marks":[{"type":"underline"}],"data":{}}]},{"nodeType":"text","value":". When a test fails, all related details — logs, screenshots — can be automatically linked to a ticket. This helps engineers respond more quickly and makes collaboration between developers and QA teams easier and more effective.","marks":[],"data":{}}]},{"nodeType":"paragraph","data":{},"content":[{"nodeType":"text","value":"3. Support for Multi-Environment Testing","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"data":{}}]},{"nodeType":"paragraph","data":{},"content":[{"nodeType":"text","value":"ReportPortal manages and monitors testing across multiple environments, including different operating systems and hardware configurations. This flexibility allows teams to run the same test suits under different conditions and compare outcomes in one dashboard, without the need for manual result collection.","marks":[],"data":{}}]},{"nodeType":"paragraph","data":{},"content":[{"nodeType":"text","value":"If a problem appears only in a specific setup — for example, on a particular OS version or hardware type — ReportPortal makes it easy to spot and investigate. This helps maintain consistent performance and reliability across all environments.","marks":[],"data":{}}]},{"nodeType":"paragraph","data":{},"content":[{"nodeType":"text","value":"4. Real-Time Visibility for Long-Running Tests","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"data":{}}]},{"nodeType":"paragraph","data":{},"content":[{"nodeType":"text","value":"Hardware testing often involves extended test suites lasting several days. ReportPortal provides ","marks":[],"data":{}},{"nodeType":"hyperlink","data":{"uri":"https://reportportal.io/docs/dashboards-and-widgets/"},"content":[{"nodeType":"text","value":"real-time visibility","marks":[{"type":"underline"}],"data":{}}]},{"nodeType":"text","value":" into test execution, enabling teams to monitor progress and identify issues immediately.","marks":[],"data":{}}]},{"nodeType":"paragraph","data":{},"content":[{"nodeType":"text","value":"Instead of waiting for an entire test run to complete, engineers can see partial results as they come in, check system stability, and stop or adjust tests when necessary. This saves time, prevents wasted resources, and helps teams react to critical issues while the tests are still running.","marks":[],"data":{}}]},{"nodeType":"paragraph","data":{},"content":[{"nodeType":"text","value":"5. Early Defect Detection and Triage","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"data":{}}]},{"nodeType":"paragraph","data":{},"content":[{"nodeType":"text","value":"In long-running test suites, ReportPortal allows teams to begin ","marks":[],"data":{}},{"nodeType":"hyperlink","data":{"uri":"https://reportportal.io/blog/defect-triage-with-reportportal/"},"content":[{"nodeType":"text","value":"defect triage","marks":[{"type":"underline"}],"data":{}}]},{"nodeType":"text","value":" as soon as a test case fails, without waiting for the entire suite to complete. This minimizes downtime and accelerates problem resolution.","marks":[],"data":{}}]},{"nodeType":"paragraph","data":{},"content":[{"nodeType":"text","value":"This early feedback loop helps testers isolate recurring issues and quickly determine whether a defect is caused by a system bug, test instability, or configuration error.","marks":[],"data":{}}]},{"nodeType":"paragraph","data":{},"content":[{"nodeType":"text","value":"By grouping similar failures and automatically labeling them, ReportPortal reduces manual work and keeps testing cycles moving smoothly.","marks":[],"data":{}}]},{"nodeType":"paragraph","data":{},"content":[{"nodeType":"text","value":"6. Enhanced Testing Efficiency","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"data":{}}]},{"nodeType":"paragraph","data":{},"content":[{"nodeType":"text","value":"By enabling parallel execution and continuous monitoring, ReportPortal optimizes the efficiency of testing processes, especially for system-level and hardware-related software. It aggregates results from multiple runs, filters repetitive data, and provides clear summaries, allowing teams to focus on what really matters — improving quality and coverage.","marks":[],"data":{}}]},{"nodeType":"paragraph","data":{},"content":[{"nodeType":"text","value":"With less time spent on manual reporting, QA engineers can focus on analysis, planning, and improving the overall testing process.","marks":[],"data":{}}]},{"nodeType":"paragraph","data":{},"content":[{"nodeType":"text","value":"7. Actionable Analytics with AI/ML","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"data":{}}]},{"nodeType":"paragraph","data":{},"content":[{"nodeType":"text","value":"ReportPortal uses AI and machine learning to analyze recurring issues, predict potential problem areas, and optimize testing strategies for system-level software. This helps reduce regression risk and supports smarter, data-driven decisions throughout the testing process.","marks":[],"data":{}}]},{"nodeType":"paragraph","data":{},"content":[{"nodeType":"text","value":"Use Case: Test Result Analysis with LLM and MCP Server","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"data":{}},{"nodeType":"text","value":"

Imagine being able to automatically analyze your test results and identify defects — directly within your favorite IDE.

